The comment does not really make sense any more. Maybe
```suggestion
  -- prerequisite typeclasses to say that `M'` is a smooth manifold over the pair `(E', H')`.
```
Same thing a few lines above and a few lines below

```suggestion
  [Algebra R S''] [IsScalarTower R R'' S''] [IsScalarTower R S S'']
```

```suggestion
variable [DecidableEq ι] [DirectedSystem G fun i j h => f i j h] 
variable {G f}
```
We should always separate binder updates from new variables. Eventually I'd like a linter enforcing this.
